## kebab variable

Converts a CamelCase string into kebab case, with optional custom delimiter (`-` by default).

TODO: Switch back to currently broken Regex w/ positive lookbehind, once avail in FF &amp; Safari (currently TC39 stage 4)

[https://github.com/tc39/proposal-regexp-lookbehind](https://github.com/tc39/proposal-regexp-lookbehind)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
kebab: Stringer<string>
```

## Example


```ts
kebab("FooBar23Baz");
// "foo-bar23-baz"

```
